track_notes:
Wonderful extended hike from Chienberg to the summit. Free parking at the starting point. Route can be shortened by starting at the Montlinger Schwamm restaurant (5 CHF parking fee).
Lazy option three: the cable car ;)
The cablecar starts in Brülisau and is visible from far. The last few metres bring you to a wide platform with marvelous outlooks and many possibilities to activate.
track_title: ... and a very short track from the top station of Kastenbahn cablecar

track_notes: Take cable car to Hoher Kasten HB/AI-005. Continue to Fänerenspitz HB/AI-008 via Kamoralp and Resspass. Descent via Eggli to Steinegg (train station). Did this combination in both directions (up and down).
I left the trail a few times due to snow and ice.

Ride the cablecar from the valley to the restaurant at Staubernkanzel. Wonderful scenic ridge hike. Also the best starting point for AI-013. There can be some snow on the trail until early May. The only problem with this hike to AI-005 -- getting to the cablecar valley station with public transport is not terribly convenient; if you park your car there, the return hike can be quite tiring!
track_title: Beautiful ridge walk from another cablecar also near AI-013
